correction_response: This tweet is potentially misleading as it implies a significant change in Twitter due to Elon Musk, but doesn't provide any specific details or evidence to support this claim. The attached images also don't seem to directly relate to the statement, adding to the confusion.
note_1_text: This is not a "Before and After" of twitter as is claimed.    The "Before" Picture is a group of people who worked on the Twitter Comms team first seen here:   https://twitter.com/juliezsteele/status/1588419360388833280    The "After" Picture is a group of engineers posted by Elon musk.   https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-11447073/Twitter-safety-czar-resigned-reveals-Elon-Musk-boosted-efforts-rid-hate-speech.html
note_2_text: Both of these photos represent only minute fraction of the Twitter work force and in no way represent the gender or racial composition of the company either before or after.
